--------------------------------
d-inline
d-block
d-inline-block


bg
--------------
bg-success -green
bg-danger -red
bg-dark -dark
bg-light - light


clearfix
---------------
class="clearfix"

to clear float, so so elements
comes after it will be under the floated elements .


position
--------

classes
-------------------------------------------
fixed-top -- element fixed at top always we scroll
sticky-top  -- element start to stick to top when reach the element by scroll
fixed-bottom








